transcription.text:
Speaker 1: Thank you for calling Viagra. This is Jimmy. How can I help you today?

Speaker 2: Yeah, Jimmy, I got a question for you.

Speaker 1: Sure.

Speaker 2: You said Viagra, isn't it?

Speaker 1: Squirrel Blue Viagra.

Speaker 2: Well, I ordered some stink through Blue, whatever it is.

Speaker 1: And they sent me – it was supposed to be Viagra ABG, I guess it is, right?

Speaker 2: Right.

Speaker 1: And what they sent me is Slid, Slid No-Fill.

Speaker 2: Slid No-Fill. Oh, okay. So let me ask you, did you – I'm speaking to Joe.

Speaker 1: Yes.

Speaker 2: Did you order online, Joe, when you did your order?

Speaker 1: Yep.

Speaker 2: Okay. I'm sorry, Joe. Yeah. I see that you did get the Viagra 50 milligrams.

Speaker 1: I also see that you got 20 of them.

Speaker 2: And you're saying that you're trying to get the AGB, is that correct?

Speaker 1: Well, that's what I ordered, and that's what it said on the email.

Speaker 2: Okay.

Speaker 1: It says 10 tablets of the new Viagra ABG item total $49.

Speaker 2: Right. And then you ordered the extra 10 too, so you got a total of 20.

Speaker 1: But you didn't get that. You got the regular generic Viagra.

Speaker 2: So let me go ahead and take care of that for you.

Speaker 1: I'm going to fix that for you right now.

Speaker 2: Bear with me one second.

Speaker 1: I want to make sure you get the correct order sent out to you.

Speaker 2: And I also noticed that you were getting the 50 milligrams.

Speaker 1: Did you want to stick with the 50 milligrams

Speaker 2: or did you want to try the 100 milligrams?

Speaker 1: I've never tried any of them, so I don't know.

Speaker 2: Okay. Well, let me do this for you.

Speaker 1: I'm going to switch that out to you and give you the best one that's out there,

Speaker 2: which is the 100 milligram, and I'm going to send you 20 of them.

Speaker 1: Okay. And I'll get that done for you today because that's what you should have got,

Speaker 2: was 20.

Speaker 1: Yeah, that's what I was thinking.

Speaker 2: So what do I do with the ones I got?

Speaker 1: You know what, they're still good Viagra,

Speaker 2: but since you have them and you opened them probably,

Speaker 1: we're not going to ask for them back.

Speaker 2: So you just go ahead and you can keep those or whatever the case may be.

Speaker 1: They do work.

Speaker 2: But I'm going to send you out the correct AGB Viagra.

Speaker 1: Okay?

Speaker 2: Okay.

Speaker 1: You should get those within the next five to seven business days.

Speaker 2: All right?

Speaker 1: All right. Thank you.

Speaker 2: Let me tell you the difference.

Speaker 1: These are going to be a white-shaped diamond pill.

Speaker 2: They look very familiar.

Speaker 1: The prescription on the bottle is going to be the same

Speaker 2: because the pills look the same too,

Speaker 1: but they're going to have the number 100 on the back of your actual pill.

Speaker 2: So that's what you want to look for.

Speaker 1: That's how you know if they're going to be the AGB.

Speaker 2: It's going to have 100 on the back of the pill.

Speaker 1: Okay?

Speaker 2: Okay.

Speaker 1: All right.

Speaker 2: Will it still say Solenafil or will it say Viagra AGB?

Speaker 1: No, it's going to say what's on the prescription

Speaker 2: because that should have been the AGB,

Speaker 1: but I can look at the order that's what the pharmacy sent.

Speaker 2: They sent the regular generic Viagra.

Speaker 1: That's why I'm sending you these out with no questions asked

Speaker 2: to make sure you get the correct ones.

Speaker 1: All right?

Speaker 2: Thank you, sir.

Speaker 1: Not a problem.

Speaker 2: Remember, the pill's going to have the 100 on the back.

Speaker 1: They're going to look very similar,

Speaker 2: but it's the 100 on the back that's going to be the difference.

Speaker 1: All right?

Speaker 2: Okay.

Speaker 1: Sounds good.

Speaker 2: Thank you, buddy.

Speaker 1: All right.

Speaker 2: Take care.

Speaker 1: No problem.

Speaker 2: Bye-bye.

Speaker 1: Bye-bye.
